entry.tran: 难以解释的事情;无法估计的事物
entry.def: An imponderable is something unknown which it is difficult or impossible to estimate or make correct guesses about.

example.ex: They are speculating on the imponderables of the future.
example.tran: 他们猜测着未来难以预见的事情。
